174
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:50,740
Call me anytime.

175
00:15:53,380 --> 00:15:54,900
I've tidied up the baby's room.

176
00:15:55,180 --> 00:15:58,140
It's a man's job to assemble
the little rocking horse.

177
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:38,060
