178
00:18:48,580 --> 00:18:49,220
Jiaxin,

179
00:18:50,580 --> 00:18:51,700
I miss you so much.

180
00:19:01,620 --> 00:19:02,260
I'm sorry

181
00:19:03,420 --> 00:19:04,540
