182
00:19:06,860 --> 00:19:07,740
After you get discharged from the hospital,

183
00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:09,900
I'll take you home, okay?

184
00:19:17,460 --> 00:19:18,900
Let's start over.

185
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:20,140
Okay?

